ttps://github.com/Shopify/packwerk/blob/main/UPGRADING.md) for details. (@AlexEvanczuk)\r\n- Removed deprecated `packwerk update` command; use `packwerk update-deprecations` instead. (@AlexEvanczuk)\r\n\r\nThank you so much for pushing this through, Alex!\r\n\r\n### Housekeeping\r\n\r\nNo housekeeping this time!\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Shopify/packwerk/releases/54085068/reactions", "total_count": 2, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 2, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "mentions_count": 1}
