g Fixes\r\n\r\n- allow running packwerk outside of application bundle (#152, @jordanstephens)\r\n- Fix https://github.com/Shopify/packwerk/issues/103 - Packwerk.yml exclude option does not work (#155, @jordanstephens)\r\n\r\n### Breaking changes\r\n\r\nnone.\r\n\r\n### Housekeeping\r\n\r\nSpecial thanks for these less glamourous, but equally helpful contributions:\r\n- bump sorbet typing levels (#151, @AlexEvanczuk)\r\n- simplify orchestration layer (#147, @kenzan100)", "mentions_count": 4}
